              incorrectFeedback: 'At 22 cal/cm², Category 2 (8 cal/cm² minimum) is insufficient — it does not cover 22 cal/cm². Category 4 is required when incident energy exceeds 25 cal/cm², which this does not. The correct category is 3: minimum 25 cal/cm² rated arc flash suit and hood.',
